description: One-of-a-kind corner unit with 1,100 sq. ft. of exclusive outdoor space! This nearly 1,700 sq. ft. loft-style duplex offers 1 bed, 1.5 baths, and bold architectural design. Soaring ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows, and bamboo floors create an airy, sun-filled vibe. The sleek chef’s kitchen features custom cabinetry, high-end appliances, granite counters, and direct access to a private patio. Downstairs, enjoy a spacious living area with beautiful custom desk and built-in shelving, designed by Samuel Anderson. The primary suite is a true retreat with a spa-like bath and an oversized walk-out patio. In-unit laundry, central A/C, and garage parking add convenience. Court Square Press is a full-service building with 24-hour concierge, outdoor pool and grilling area, media room and gym.  One Garage parking space rounds out this unique home. Steps to top dining, bars, and public transit—this one-of-a-kind home defines Southie luxury. Don’t miss it!
